Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.06,0:01:51.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是让人心旷神怡的风景啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.33,0:01:53.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边就是汤乃鹭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.31,0:01:57.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦  看起来能拍出好电影来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.72,0:02:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.83,0:02:03.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  我是伊佐美
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.01,0:02:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.46,0:02:14.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过开张以来  还真是热闹非凡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.23,0:02:22.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家的意见我都听过了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.56,0:02:23.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他还有什么补充吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.47,0:02:26.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我们现在就听听年轻人的意见
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.76,0:02:29.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看她们对于温泉旅馆有些什么期望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.46,0:02:31.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,权当给我们做参考好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.01,0:02:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  谁说只要乖乖躲在后面听就好…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.79,0:02:38.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说你们的心里话哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.77,0:02:39.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怎么样的？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.55,0:02:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…总而言之就是要便宜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.27,0:02:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能吃好多自己爱吃的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.22,0:02:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得这样的温泉旅馆比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.45,0:02:50.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说具体些
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.08,0:02:52.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常便宜的自助餐形式
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.98,0:02:56.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从早到晚肉啊蛋糕啊都随便吃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.55,0:03:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后还有豪华观光大巴直通汤乃鹭什么的！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.62,0:03:02.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.04,0:03:06.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有个用温泉水的室内泳池就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.71,0:03:09.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯  绝对要一个游泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.11,0:03:12.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为没准就有客人希望一天二十四小时都能游泳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.96,0:03:14.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  一定有的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.35,0:03:17.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是大巴里还能任吃蛋糕就最棒了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.37,0:03:21.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备完成
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.09,0:03:25.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那按这个给老板娘做一番演说吧  少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.50,0:03:27.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.16,0:03:28.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.66,0:03:32.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少爷这么没自信怎么成
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.12,0:03:35.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演说者十足的干劲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.32,0:03:38.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是说服对方的过程中所必须的重要因素
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.73,0:03:40.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.59,0:03:46.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信老板娘一定能理解我们的计划是对于喜翠庄的敬意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.70,0:03:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦  我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.75,0:03:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.95,0:03:56.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这地方实在是很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.59,0:03:57.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.43,0:04:00.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.25,0:04:11.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜翠庄需承担的投资额就只有总制作费的十分之一而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.03,0:04:13.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.19,0:04:15.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是起死回生的一步棋…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.75,0:04:17.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宣传效果是出类拔萃的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.20,0:04:20.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大部分看了这电影的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.40,0:04:22.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都会希望能来喜翠庄住一次
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.89,0:04:25.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是便会冲着汤乃鹭而来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.67,0:04:28.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然我们谁也没法保证每个地方都能面面俱到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.12,0:04:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我长年以来的直觉告诉我  这里有…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.32,0:04:34.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请让我和少当家的单独谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.85,0:04:35.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.99,0:04:38.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  我也一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.78,0:04:40.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.99,0:04:42.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,崇子小姐也一起比较…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.26,0:04:43.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.80,0:04:50.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊  我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.66,0:04:54.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就让老板娘和少爷两人好好畅谈一番吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.21,0:04:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小菜要做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.80,0:05:00.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和弟弟们去海边
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.47,0:05:01.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪花呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.01,0:05:04.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我暑假里就是干活
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.88,0:05:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一起去海边吧  去海边  海边可好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.94,0:05:12.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢  要不我也去看看小菜的弟弟们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.01,0:05:15.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.33,0:05:18.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍电影啊  电影
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.11,0:05:19.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.67,0:05:22.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是迟钝的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.52,0:05:24.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要在喜翠庄拍电影了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.98,0:05:26.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶……
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.46,0:05:30.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  糟糕  怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.19,0:05:32.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得快点回家告诉他们才行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.22,0:05:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…啊啊…我会扮演什么角色呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.83,0:05:41.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍电影？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.07,0:05:43.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  在喜翠庄
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.18,0:05:45.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.66,0:06:01.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  老妈你也清楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.21,0:06:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不光是我们店的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.73,0:06:08.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去整个汤乃鹭温泉街…就遭殃了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.49,0:06:12.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当崇子小姐跟我提起拍摄电影的事宜时
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.97,0:06:14.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得那样倒挺不错的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.50,0:06:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无所谓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.74,0:06:19.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次就按你喜欢来做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.10,0:06:20.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.43,0:06:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总而言之这次是导演的强烈意向
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.83,0:06:29.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是重要角色
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.89,0:06:33.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也考虑让拍摄地现场的人员来担当
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.22,0:06:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,导演下次来时
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.23,0:06:38.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会对大家做一个简单的试镜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.08,0:06:40.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经心跳个不停了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.67,0:06:43.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个暑假看来会非常棒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.22,0:06:44.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.08,0:06:47.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是由高台跳水的奥运选手转变而成的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.76,0:06:49.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一名华丽的女间谍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.81,0:06:52.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  小民想演怎样的角色？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.26,0:06:54.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.25,0:06:55.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厨师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.62,0:06:57.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.94,0:07:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是电影哦  能演你想演的角色哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.20,0:07:02.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如女警
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.56,0:07:04.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又比如乘务员大姐姐之类的 还有护士…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.17,0:07:05.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.44,0:07:10.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是小民  真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.92,0:07:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.83,0:07:20.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制作电影的事宜好像全权交给少爷负责了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.22,0:07:20.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.33,0:07:24.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电影  可真不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.52,0:07:29.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那部《干枯花朵》里的加贺麻里子  真的很可爱哪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.13,0:07:32.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀电六  你还没枯萎吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.22,0:07:34.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不敢当
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.73,0:07:42.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为你是在地方执笔的人士  所以我才提出这个请求
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.99,0:07:45.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四十页纸  有十分钟之多吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.29,0:07:46.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,务必请你帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.06,0:07:51.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做出能够让人感受到这块土地最质朴的温暖的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.82,0:07:55.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不和导演先生还有主剧作家们开会商讨什么的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.84,0:07:57.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.13,0:07:59.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基础设定和情节由我来负责
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.49,0:08:02.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能先请你稍微写一些  作为我们的草案呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.06,0:08:06.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基于你的草案再和导演做深入探讨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.72,0:08:07.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.02,0:08:13.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  我记得这里传承着什么雪洞祭来着的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.08,0:08:17.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这类描写能不能自然地穿插进去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.42,0:08:18.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次郎丸先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.71,0:08:23.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实这次委托你也是少爷答应参与电影拍摄的一个条件
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.34,0:08:26.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真  真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.08,0:08:29.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我次郎丸太郎肝脑涂地在所不辞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.42,0:08:36.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,设备机能是否正常  会由专门的从业人员来确认
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.77,0:08:40.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想拜托你们做的是清扫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.67,0:08:43.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是…游泳池？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.94,0:08:45.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前好像是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.56,0:08:46.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.78,0:08:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是要我们来做清扫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.50,0:08:52.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个游泳池在电影中也是一个必须的场景
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.45,0:08:55.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是少爷参与拍摄的一个条件
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.13,0:08:59.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少爷  有什么要吩咐的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.23,0:09:04.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里将要成为电影中一个重要的舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.43,0:09:05.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托各位认真清扫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.95,0:09:08.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要游泳池呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.79,0:09:12.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪花你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.44,0:09:13.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是描写夏天的电影啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.16,0:09:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到夏天必然就是泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.66,0:09:17.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到泳池必然就是夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.07,0:09:18.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.80,0:09:22.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有做错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.59,0:09:56.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总而言之  清扫泳池就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.50,0:10:08.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.05,0:10:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  我该怎么向您道谢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.29,0:10:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能得到这样一个机会…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.70,0:10:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机会总是会光顾有准备的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.72,0:10:22.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅仅如此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.33,0:10:24.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.13,0:10:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们彼此都一路努力过来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.82,0:10:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.94,0:10:31.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让人好生心酸的人生  我们此前屡屡狼狈不堪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.67,0:10:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还一直竹篮打水一场空
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.74,0:10:34.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.64,0:10:35.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这也就到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.44,0:10:39.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们心中有着一道尽管微弱  但却无比真实的光辉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.72,0:10:43.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它诉说着我们至今为止一切的所作所为都没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.91,0:10:44.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.68,0:10:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.41,0:10:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你稿费的一半以及版权税
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.36,0:10:54.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就由我们收下以充当你滞留至今的房费
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.25,0:10:56.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.21,0:10:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.05,0:11:05.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那好  我去和制作组联络一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.11,0:11:07.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后会和导演一起再来的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.45,0:11:09.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松村导演要大驾光临吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.14,0:11:13.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一作《湿透的纽扣》真的很棒呢  第二作也…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.43,0:11:18.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两位主演说也想尽快看到这个将作为舞台的旅馆的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.87,0:11:19.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.13,0:11:22.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的契约到那时再签
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.13,0:11:23.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭候您的大驾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.88,0:11:31.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭候您的大驾！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.49,0:12:08.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板娘马上就来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.68,0:12:09.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请先进…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.35,0:12:11.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在这里等好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.12,0:12:12.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.99,0:12:14.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我来倾听吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.19,0:12:20.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  请这边走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.24,0:12:29.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请务必让我们参加这个绝佳的方案
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.79,0:12:33.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这次的电影背景设定在汤乃鹭全体会更好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.80,0:12:36.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的没错  在这经济不景气的世道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.56,0:12:37.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赞助资金分担一下的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.97,0:12:40.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜翠庄也会轻松不少吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.49,0:12:41.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错没错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.58,0:12:42.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错没错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.86,0:12:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必担心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.82,0:12:49.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们想要帮忙的心意非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.76,0:12:52.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次的外景已经确定在喜翠庄了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.85,0:12:54.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点不打算更改
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.18,0:13:00.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  为什么我们要出钱宣传喜翠庄呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.68,0:13:03.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不用勉强来赞助了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.57,0:13:17.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪花  再集中一点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.55,0:13:24.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候变成那么了不起的少爷了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.83,0:13:27.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然全部一个人来做  真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.58,0:13:32.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之已经确认今后不管发生什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.18,0:13:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,责任都由喜翠庄来承担了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.93,0:13:49.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎坚决地回绝了其他旅馆的意见呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.46,0:13:53.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  少爷最近好像变了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.66,0:13:56.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像越来越有自信了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.68,0:13:59.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然男人只有经过风雨才能成大器呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.37,0:14:02.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电影吗…真是一次豪赌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.29,0:14:05.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是莲先生决定要演什么角色了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.71,0:14:09.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  莲先生也要出演吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.77,0:14:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,导演说希望拍摄地现场的人员也能出演
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.98,0:14:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害  那…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.72,0:14:16.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.37,0:14:19.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彻  你手上的活怎么停下了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.82,0:14:21.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.07,0:14:24.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  回自己岗位上去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.22,0:14:30.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去削萝卜皮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.21,0:14:33.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪巴小姐说了那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.58,0:14:34.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连彻先生也起劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.53,0:14:37.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电影电影
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.41,0:14:39.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厨师出演电影有什么用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.35,0:14:43.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  彻先生的话一定会很上镜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.29,0:14:46.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.42,0:14:50.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,all right
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.90,0:14:57.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害  起重机啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.37,0:14:59.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然电影必须要用起重机呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.05,0:15:05.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是这次的主演女角  末广小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.45,0:15:07.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.99,0:15:11.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然本尊就是不一样呢  小菜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.20,0:15:10.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38}请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.81,0:15:21.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样  从那天起就开始测试摄影了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.74,0:15:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好紧张呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.03,0:15:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静一点  绪花
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.73,0:15:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凉茶沏好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.86,0:15:40.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.53,0:16:01.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.83,0:16:03.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.98,0:16:06.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里真是家不错的旅馆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.68,0:16:08.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我非常喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.69,0:16:11.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是  真想下次利用私人时间来一次呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.26,0:16:13.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢夸奖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.64,0:16:16.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是非常久远的建筑了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.84,0:16:19.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维护管理起来很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.62,0:16:25.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  我接手的时候已经有60年的历史了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.83,0:16:27.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,60年吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.63,0:16:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟那么长时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.64,0:16:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总会在看不见的地方出现裂痕之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.70,0:16:33.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.39,0:16:35.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  老板娘也在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.51,0:16:38.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,末广小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.55,0:16:41.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问能签个名让我们挂在走廊上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.06,0:16:42.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.59,0:16:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.60,0:16:53.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是真亏老板娘会同意这次摄影呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.18,0:16:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说直接就同意了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.14,0:16:58.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好老板娘其实也想出演
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.59,0:17:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有可能～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.93,0:17:08.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  由我来代替主角？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.97,0:17:10.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是测试下摄像机而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.97,0:17:13.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.25,0:17:16.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主角似乎是误点了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.18,0:17:18.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是便宜你了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.47,0:17:21.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和末广小姐牵着手  just marriage conform
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.87,0:17:23.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.99,0:17:26.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少爷  要表演得出色一点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.89,0:17:32.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.10,0:17:36.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,崇子小姐  准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.57,0:17:38.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.73,0:17:41.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  再靠近一点 好 很好很好 nice
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.44,0:17:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,导演坚决要一个结实一点的男性
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.32,0:17:47.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.84,0:17:56.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.54,0:17:58.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别玩了  好好做呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.70,0:18:03.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小民  快点快点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.13,0:18:17.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.40,0:18:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.41,0:18:24.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  小民也休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.18,0:18:33.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.43,0:18:35.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.10,0:18:36.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过变干净了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.91,0:18:39.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  变干净不少了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.31,0:18:40.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还差一点了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.72,0:18:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  还差一点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.32,0:18:46.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.18,0:18:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小民
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.09,0:18:53.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很感谢崇子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.26,0:18:58.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电影呀  我一个人的话绝对搞不定的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.32,0:19:24.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.61,0:19:26.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.06,0:19:28.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.78,0:19:31.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.56,0:19:48.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还记得一起去电影研究会的自我作品发表会的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.43,0:19:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大学的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.79,0:19:52.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,崇子小姐一年级的秋天
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.90,0:19:56.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不记得了呢  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.31,0:19:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.32,0:19:59.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.48,0:20:00.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.83,0:20:05.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个一直在拍泳装女初中生的变态电影
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.91,0:20:07.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个时代的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.12,0:20:08.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个导演绝对要去警察局了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.14,0:20:12.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我的处女作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.38,0:20:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.12,0:20:16.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是最后一作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.13,0:20:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在电影研究会打算拍长篇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.76,0:20:24.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来的导演却突然不干了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.08,0:20:28.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是成员也没了干劲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.51,0:20:29.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.67,0:20:32.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果变成我一个人的拍摄了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.16,0:20:36.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该说是自己原来的样貌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.14,0:20:38.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是真面目
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.03,0:20:42.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那几个孩子有好好干活吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.16,0:20:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么想  姐姐都要比我适合经营喜翠庄
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.90,0:20:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和老板娘都是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.95,0:20:55.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四十万君…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.48,0:21:01.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个称呼  自大学后第一次听到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.81,0:21:04.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.17,0:21:08.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去沏杯茶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.18,0:21:13.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐好像是叫皋月小姐是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.07,0:21:17.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐的头脑灵活
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.86,0:21:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从小就很会说话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.86,0:21:23.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有魅力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.52,0:21:26.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在学校也很有人气
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.33,0:21:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐非常闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.29,0:21:31.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又漂亮又聪明
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.59,0:21:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得是活在别的世界的人一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.76,0:21:38.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像是…和我无关的人
